com.bmd.android.collection

Class CompatCollections

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmd.android.collection.CompatCollections
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JellyBeanCollections

    public class CompatCollections
extends Object
    This utility class creates objects wrapping an Android sparse collection, such as SparseArray and SparseArrayCompat, to give it the base functionalities of an Iterable object.

    Created by davide on 3/9/14.
